item.title: How do i change the home teleport for my rsps
item.dc:creator: @xXThatOneSkaterKidXx xXThatOneSkaterKidXx
item.description:
@xXThatOneSkaterKidXx wrote:

Okay first you need to open up OptionClicking.java
Once opened, search for the keywords “home”
Right under where it says home is a bunch of coords in perenthesis
simply put the coords of the place you want to change it to, save, exit, compile, and you should be done. (:
